{"tid":1981220,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【黃皮白心 你係隻蕉】 MC Jin作rap鬧特朗普係鴨 網民：有膽燒美國護照移去武漢住","createTime":"2020-04-20T14:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T14:30:14.000Z","uid":242537,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"65a3484150408eefee7962b1057613932017c4ed","tid":1981220,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/QMe65SyBI2Mxv6oYphZs9gJMcU8=/802x1231/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/HAG7VHJJGUUGUBQVYXIGTULBNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FQMe65SyBI2Mxv6oYphZs9gJMcU8%3D%2F802x1231%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FHAG7VHJJGUUGUBQVYXIGTULBNA.jpg&h=819abca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200419/LVCKHRRIIFXDKAPXVWPW63OXG4/?fbclid=IwAR23Gsueu-sJtQiR-E9zDFy2oEi-and5s0Dfz4UBBICYZi_egBdUM5g6WDE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200419%2FLVCKHRRIIFXDKAPXVWPW63OXG4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR23Gsueu-sJtQiR-E9zDFy2oEi-and5s0Dfz4UBBICYZi_egBdUM5g6WDE&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=adf65c22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200419%2FLVCKHRRIIFXDKAPXVWPW63OXG4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR23Gsueu-sJtQiR-E9zDFy2oEi-and5s0Dfz4UBBICYZi_egBdUM5g6WDE&h=0a0d32c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200419/LVCKHRRIIFXDKAPXVWPW63OXG4/?fbclid=IwAR23Gsueu-sJtQiR-E9zDFy2oEi-and5s0Dfz4UBBICYZi_egBdUM5g6WDE</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢疫情全球大爆發，播毒源頭的大陸近月聲稱疫情受到控制，而近月的重災區就是歐洲及美國。當中美國情況惡劣，至今已有72多萬確診個案，死亡人數已有3萬7千多人，美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）日前警告，如果證實大陸蓄意隱瞞疫情造成武肺全球大流行，中國須面對後果，而武肺更令外國人一見華人避之則吉，引起一陣「排華潮」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/YOpGj4G1wyy5_OTeENq56E2bk0c=/802x341/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ALRADJCPUEAMSXGKTRQPNBXTXU.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FYOpGj4G1wyy5_OTeENq56E2bk0c%3D%2F802x341%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FALRADJCPUEAMSXGKTRQPNBXTXU.jpg&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=9a419737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/YOpGj4G1wyy5_OTeENq56E2bk0c=/802x341/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ALRADJCPUEAMSXGKTRQPNBXTXU.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身為美國華裔的藝人歐陽靖（MC Jin）是正宗的「ABC」（American Born Chinese）近年活躍大陸的綜藝節目，更憑《中國有嘻哈》入到大陸市場賺人仔，對於近月的排華潮已多次發聲，呼籲亞裔人士要小心，再在3月底，拍片怒斥特朗普的「中國病毒」言論，強調現在須要團結：「再不是種族敵對，而是善良與惡魔的分別。病毒是病毒，我們不能控制，但我們能夠控制如何應對。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/25P1hASDigHTPo0XJD04eo0mZdk=/802x496/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/OUEFRIL7DDFZMZQYJPUWQT7X3A.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F25P1hASDigHTPo0XJD04eo0mZdk%3D%2F802x496%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FOUEFRIL7DDFZMZQYJPUWQT7X3A.jpg&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=9d93aa36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/25P1hASDigHTPo0XJD04eo0mZdk=/802x496/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/OUEFRIL7DDFZMZQYJPUWQT7X3A.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來MC Jin日前鬧完總統特朗普分化外，更自製了Rap歌邊唱邊數Donald Trump，歌詞提到現在須要是團結和平，指死亡是沒有種族顏色之分，他的8歲兒子問他為何別人稱武肺是「中國病毒」，MC Jin表示痛心，指言論是無知，更指行為背後是魔鬼推動，疫情越來嚴峻，更看起來沒有好轉的趨勢，更指特朗普是「唐老鴨」（Donald Duck），如鴨子頭腦簡單，希望他在大選大敗：「my president Donald simple and plain as a duck, I sincerely pray that comin' election day he gets trumped」並指特朗普將華人當笨蛋，更揚言自己可能只是一隻羔羊，但絕對不會掛名「代罪」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/fw-80wf95slugqvz6-5cm7c6H34=/802x800/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/5JWAHSLPRJROZEA5YUSQERJT6A.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Ffw-80wf95slugqvz6-5cm7c6H34%3D%2F802x800%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F5JWAHSLPRJROZEA5YUSQERJT6A.jpg&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=11fd5702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/fw-80wf95slugqvz6-5cm7c6H34=/802x800/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/5JWAHSLPRJROZEA5YUSQERJT6A.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首歌一出，有網民在他的社交平台讚好支持，不過就有大量網民在轉貼此報道的帖文就不認同，更有網民叫他「燒咗你本美國護照，搬去武漢住啦！」、「 垃圾，返中國住，放棄美國國籍先講自己愛國」、「返回早國，Rap = RMB」、「你可以講特朗普係鴨！但你敢唔敢講習xx係熊？」、「因為佢個仔喺美國大，聽慣真話」等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forumd.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7221862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforumd.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D7221862&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=951dba25\" target=\"_blank\">https://forumd.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7221862</a>"},{"pid":"399b0e22095242025862145d5e24b77a3df92f31","tid":1981220,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"好失望"},{"pid":"4affd1c7fc874f469778d93226dbcfd34e0b94eb","tid":1981220,"uid":154054,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:04:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實個問題唔撚係因為源頭係中國<br />\n而係因為佢地隱瞞疫情搞到全世界都仆街阿MC Jin<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6dbe0b331e988f3cb41091f1b7ae414665ce8134","tid":1981220,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re